  "number": 387,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/387",
  "title": "priceRanges: Making BEM classes more consistent",
  "body": "I was looking at theming the priceRanges widget, and there are a few things that needs to be updated.\n\nIt currently generates the following markup:\n\n``` html\n<div class=\"ais-price-ranges\">\n  <div class=\"ais-price-ranges--header ais-header\">Header</div>\n  <div class=\"ais-price-ranges--body\">\n    <a class=\"ais-price-ranges--range\" href=\"...\">\n      $3 - $13\n      <span></span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"ais-price-ranges--range ais-price-ranges--range__active\" href=\"...\">\n      $13 - $40\n      <span></span>\n    </a>\n    <form class=\"ais-price-ranges--form\">\n      <label><span>$</span><span> </span><input class=\"ais-price-ranges--input\" /></label>\n      <span> </span><span>to</span><span> </span>\n      <label><span>$</span><span> </span><input class=\"ais-price-ranges--input\" /></label>\n      <span> </span><button class=\"ais-price-ranges--button\">Go</button>\n    </form>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ais-price-ranges--footer ais-footer\">Footer</div>\n</div>\n```\n\nFirst, it seems that we have two issues:\n1. The count is not displayed in the `ais-price-range--range`.\n2. It seems there are way too many useless `span`s here. Do you have any idea what they are for?\n\nAnd I would also:\n- [x] Rename the `ais-price-ranges--range` to `ais-price-ranges--item`\n- [x] Wrap them in a `ais-price-ranges--list`, to stay consistent with other widgets (and being able to share styling easily).\n- [x] Add `ais-price-ranges--form-label` (?) to the `label` inside the bottom `form`.\n",
  "created_at": "2015-10-29T11:01:37Z",
